sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as End User
    participant Web as Demo.Web
    participant BFF as Demo.Bff
    participant Auth as NexusAuth

    User->>Web: 打开前端并点击登录
    Web->>BFF: GET /api/auth/login
    BFF->>Auth: GET /.well-known/openid-configuration
    Auth-->>BFF: 返回 discovery
    BFF-->>Web: 返回 302 到 /connect/authorize<br/>携带 state + nonce + PKCE
    Web-->>User: 浏览器跳转到登录页

    User->>Auth: 输入用户名密码并确认授权
    Auth->>Auth: 校验用户身份<br/>校验 client_id / redirect_uri / PKCE 要求
    Auth-->>BFF: 302 回调 /signin-oidc?code=...&state=...

    BFF->>BFF: 校验 state<br/>取出 code_verifier
    BFF->>Auth: POST /connect/token<br/>grant_type=authorization_code<br/>client_assertion(private_key_jwt)<br/>code + code_verifier
    Auth->>Auth: 校验 client_assertion<br/>- 签名 / JWKS<br/>- iss == sub == client_id<br/>- aud == /connect/token<br/>- alg == RS256<br/>- jti 防重放
    Auth->>Auth: 校验授权码与 PKCE
    Auth-->>BFF: access_token + id_token + refresh_token

    BFF->>Auth: GET /.well-known/jwks.json
    Auth-->>BFF: 返回签名公钥
    BFF->>BFF: 验证 id_token<br/>校验 nonce
    BFF->>Auth: GET /connect/userinfo<br/>Bearer access_token
    Auth-->>BFF: 返回用户 Claims
    BFF->>BFF: 建立本地 Cookie Session
    BFF-->>Web: 返回登录成功状态
    Web->>BFF: GET /api/profile
    BFF->>BFF: Cookie 中间件自动验证会话<br/>access_token 接近过期时触发 refresh_token
    BFF->>Auth: POST /connect/token<br/>grant_type=refresh_token<br/>refresh_token=...<br/>client_assertion(private_key_jwt)
    Auth->>Auth: 校验 refresh_token 与 client 绑定<br/>吊销旧 refresh_token 并签发新 token
    Auth-->>BFF: 新的 access_token + refresh_token
    BFF->>BFF: 更新 Cookie Session 中的 session_payload
    BFF-->>Web: 返回当前登录用户信息
